The management of Kaduna Polytechnic has terminated the appointment of a former Head of Department, Civil Engineering, Engr. Danjuma Alhassan over allegation of sexual harassment of a female student of the institution. The Governing Council of the institution had at its 91st regular meeting held on 30th January, 2020, approved the termination of the lecturerâ€™s appointment. A letter to that effect was issued on 31st January, 2020 by the deputy registrar, information & protocol for the of the institution, Samuel Y. Obochi.